  "id": "RAW_d30bb0d8",
  "title": "Bug 变奖励：AI 的小失误，揭开创造力真相！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&mid=2652633752&idx=3&sn=fd3b7a186525a3a0a7e88893859cfbbd",
  "date": "2025-10-12 09:14:00",
  "author": "新智元",
  "siteName": "新智元",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3226713d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb13PK7P1RbtdYGPvMEGtxJibDASfIft1FhLozCktojTiaMOrnicvLC1D2Ez3nOq7yLBfR66Aia3Ztp9vg%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></strong><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：倾倾</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px; line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: normal;\">扩散模型本该只是复制机器，却一次次画出「六指人像」甚至是陌生场景。最新研究发现，AI的「创造力」其实是架构里的副作用。有学者大胆推测人类的灵感或许也是如此。当灵感成了固定公式，人类和AI的差别还有多少？</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">你一定见过那些奇怪的AI画：人物手上多出几根手指、脸部细节怪异，却又带着某种说不出的新鲜感。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这让人产生一个疑问：扩散模型明明只「复刻」，为什么还能画出前所未见的作品？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最新一项研究给出了答案：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其实，AI的创造力并非「神来之笔」，而是模型架构的副作用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">明明只会复制，AI为何还能创作？</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">扩散模型的任务很简单：把数字噪声还原成训练过的图像。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">就像把一幅画放入碎纸机，直到只剩下一堆细小的灰尘，然后将碎片重新拼凑到一起。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">照理说，它应该只会生成「复制品」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可现实却让研究者大跌眼镜。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">DALL·E、Imagen、Stable Diffusion这些模型，画出的不是「翻版」，而是全新的图像：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不同元素被组合在一起，构成前所未见的场景。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">更令人意外的是，这些拼贴并不是毫无意义的杂乱色块，而是带着语义的完整作品。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505138712\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.32187938288920054\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1426\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1426\" data-height=\"459\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"181\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b19d0904&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb13PK7P1RbtdYGPvMEGtxJibx9icT06qvPoib8JLUNBaHPjUwo7FzdLT74xNNjQcb70AlgKW7oQt9Ayw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">DALL·E 2制作了这些「金鱼在海滩上啜饮可口可乐」的图像。这个由 OpenAI创建的程序可能从未遇到过类似的图像，但它仍然可以自行生成这样的图像。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">还记得那些在社交平台疯传的「AI多手指人像」吗？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">有些图看上去像是超现实主义的画——人物手上莫名其妙多出几根手指，但整体仍旧保持了清晰的结构感。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505138713\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9243589743589744\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"780\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"780\" data-height=\"721\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"534\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=9017aceb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb13PK7P1RbtdYGPvMEGtxJibEgujZzoVNiaQ0ykVqs2oLWIfZPX9FwMoxvGZEQZic2gvpL3AmnXicL8pA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这类怪异产物，一度被当成笑料，却也让科学家警觉：模型为什么会「即兴发挥」？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Giulio Biroli将这种现象称为「扩散模型的悖论」：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">「如果它们真的只是记忆，就不该有创造力；可它们偏偏能画出前所未见的东西」。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">那么，AI的创造力到底是从哪里来的？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">六指人像背后的「bug奖励」</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在最新研究里，两位物理学家给出了一个颇为出乎意料的答案：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">AI的「创造力」，其实是它架构里的副作用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505138680\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5231350330500472\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1059\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1059\" data-height=\"554\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"294\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8cb2be12&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb13PK7P1RbtdYGPvMEGtxJibqsiaBBK2NuBGwickdK2icqvr3VnZNXbGdUP3QwgFZibVp0bGcvbFic4ibWXA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">扩散模型在生成图像时，依赖两条严格的规则：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">第一条叫做局部性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它在绘制过程中，并不会通盘考虑整张画面，而是一次只关注一个小小的像素「拼块」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">就像拼图时，你盯着一块颜色相近的小碎片，却不会去想它最终会出现在整幅画的哪个角落。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">第二条叫做平移等变性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果输入图像整体往左或往右挪动几个像素，模型生成的画面也必须跟着同步移动。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这是它保持图像结构连贯的方式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这两条机制，本来是扩散模型在「去噪」时的限制条件。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究者一度认为这是缺陷，会让模型没法生成完美的复制品。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505138681\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5709123757904245\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1107\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1107\" data-height=\"632\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"321\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d0557b96&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb13PK7P1RbtdYGPvMEGtxJib7GUyb0C05KBGD4JPUvvVlQ1ARjEjgteHdYdSR4sq9R3bicUCXOLI2mQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可事实证明，正是这种「不完美」，反而让AI无法完全依赖记忆，必须在局部的拼贴里即兴重组。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这就导致了，手指可能多长了几根，元素可能拼接得有点怪异，但整体画面却意外生出了新意。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">也就是说，AI 的创造力，并不是额外设计出来的能力，而是它架构必然带来的副作用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">ELS方程机：创造力的数学化证明</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果说AI的创造力真是副作用，那要如何证明？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">斯坦福大学的研究生Mason Kamb和导师Surya Ganguli，进行了一次实验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505138682\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3366336633663367\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"404\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"404\" data-height=\"540\" data-backw=\"404\" data-backh=\"540\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=69b2dc6a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb13PK7P1RbtdYGPvMEGtxJibGItjmk2hngSSATWMMfPMxN2zx5UOrEJiaTQpicyM4ao4COqkQnFObuPg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505138695\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.344139650872818\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"401\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"401\" data-height=\"539\" data-backw=\"401\" data-backh=\"539\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fed4c083&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb13PK7P1RbtdYGPvMEGtxJibVibVVbx7cVA3CWYj2W0tuSCNmoIhW3JYiaKx6tVFXDO4MYoIu6RDI3gA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他们基于那两条规则构建了一套纯粹的数学系统，命名为ELS方程机（Equivariant Local Score machine）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这个系统的特别之处在于，它不依赖海量训练数据，也没有任何黑箱深度网络。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它是一套方程，用来预测当噪声一步步被「去除」时，图像会如何拼合。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然后，他们把同一组噪声图像同时输入ELS方程机和真实的扩散模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">结果令人震惊：ELS方程机生成的结果，与扩散模型的输出平均重合度高达 90%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在机器学习领域，这几乎是前所未有的精度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505138688\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.9437751004016064\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"249\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"249\" data-height=\"235\" data-backw=\"249\" data-backh=\"235\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d945da59&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb13PK7P1RbtdYGPvMEGtxJibyRCRZJjwAH0bMaG0OlqDE7JJZWdecbHdHyl4F8OblkbsVpCwbsVIQA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Ganguli感叹道：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">「这就像是用一组公式，写下了创造力的来源。」</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所谓的「AI创造力」，并不是神秘的灵感，而是局部性与等变性在动态运行中必然产生的产物。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">只要满足这两个条件，「创造」就会自动出现。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">AI的小失误，揭开人类创造力的秘密</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这项研究不仅揭开了扩散模型的秘密，还让人联想到生命系统。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Mason Kamb之所以产生这个灵感，是因为他长期研究形态发生——也就是胚胎如何从一团细胞，自我组装成器官和肢体。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在这个过程中，细胞只是根据身边邻居的信号做出局部反应。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">大多数时候，这种自组织能顺利生成一个正常的身体，但偶尔也会出错——比如多长出几根手指。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当Kamb看到扩散模型生成的那些「AI多指人像」时，他立刻联想到胚胎发育里的这种「局部拼贴错误」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这说明，AI的创造力，本质上和生物的自组织过程，有着惊人的相似。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究者甚至提出一个更大胆的类比：人类的创造力，也许和AI并没有本质不同。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"505138689\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4851063829787234\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1410\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-width=\"1410\" data-height=\"684\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"273\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=507b71c8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb13PK7P1RbtdYGPvMEGtxJibnV4swLibSkrVl46p650fTIBwqBQgInoeviakSwe9gPIevicGMmz96yQYA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">我们的大脑，并不是凭空冒出灵感，而是在有限的经验和记忆中，不断拼接、补全、想象，最后产出新东西。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">正是这偶尔的错误与缺口，反而成为创新的源泉。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">正如IBM研究员Benjamin Hoover所说：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">「人类和AI的创造力，可能都根植于对世界的不完整理解。」</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-top: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">创造力未必是高高在上的天赋，它也可能是一种副作用，一种「不完美」带来的意外之喜。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">当「创造力」能被一组公式写下，人类和机器的界限也愈发模糊了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">或许，真正的灵感，从来不是天才的特权，而是「不完美」的副产物。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究揭示的，不只是AI的密秘密。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">也许是在提醒我们：创造，往往生长于偏差之中。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\">\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://www.wired.com/story/researchers-uncover-hidden-ingredients-behind-ai-creativity/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wired.com/story/researchers-uncover-hidden-ingredients-behind-ai-creativity/</a></span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color:rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;\"><a href=\"https://www.quantamagazine.org/researchers-uncover-hidden-ingredients-behind-ai-creativity-20250630/\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.quantamagazine.org/researchers-uncover-hidden-ingredients-behind-ai-creativity-20250630/</a></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "扩散模型中的 AI“创造力”并非神来之笔，而是其架构中局部性与平移等变性限制的意外副作用，这一发现可能也揭示了人类创造力的本质。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "扩散模型中的 AI“创造力”并非神来之笔，而是其架构中局部性与平移等变性限制的意外副作用，这一发现可能也揭示了人类创造力的本质。",
  "summary": "文章深入探讨了扩散模型（如 DALL·E、Stable Diffusion）为何能生成前所未见的创新图像，而非简单的复制品。研究指出，AI 的“创造力”并非有意设计，而是其底层架构中“局部性”和“平移等变性”这两个限制条件的意外副作用。局部性是指模型在生成图像时仅关注小块像素，不考虑整体画面；平移等变性则要求图像平移时输出也同步移动。正是这种“不完美”迫使 AI 在局部拼贴中进行即兴重组，从而产生新颖但有时怪异的图像（如多指人像）。斯坦福大学的研究团队通过构建 ELS 方程机这一纯数学系统，验证了这一理论，其生成结果与真实扩散模型高度吻合，证明了“创造力”可由特定架构规则推导。文章进一步将此发现类比于生物的自组织过程和人类的创造力，暗示人类的灵感也可能源于对世界的不完整理解和经验的拼接重组，将创造力重新定义为一种源于“不完美”的副产物。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 扩散模型的“创造力”是其架构副作用而非设计能力。",
      "explanation": "扩散模型因“局部性”和“平移等变性”限制，无法完全记忆，被迫在局部即兴重组，从而产生新颖图像，如多指人像或陌生场景。"
    },
    {
      "point": "ELS 方程机通过数学证明 AI 创造力源于架构规则。",
      "explanation": "斯坦福大学的 ELS 方程机在无训练数据下，基于局部性和平移等变性，能以 90%精度复现扩散模型输出，揭示创造力的数学本质。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 的创造力机制与生物自组织及人类灵感有惊人相似之处。",
      "explanation": "AI 生成多指人像与胚胎发育的局部错误类似，暗示人类创造力也可能源于对世界的不完整理解和经验的拼接重组，是“不完美”的副产物。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "扩散模型本该只是复制机器，却一次次画出「六指人像」甚至是陌生场景。最新研究发现，AI 的「创造力」其实是架构里的副作用。",
    "Giulio Biroli 将这种现象称为「扩散模型的悖论」：'如果它们真的只是记忆，就不该有创造力；可它们偏偏能画出前所未见的东西'。",
    "正是这种「不完美」，反而让 AI 无法完全依赖记忆，必须在局部的拼贴里即兴重组。这就导致了，手指可能多长了几根，元素可能拼接得有点怪异，但整体画面却意外生出了新意。",
    "Ganguli 感叹道：'这就像是用一组公式，写下了创造力的来源。'",
    "人类和 AI 的创造力，可能都根植于对世界的不完整理解。"
  ],
